title: Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices: Seasonal Food for Bulgaria
notes:
The Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices category "Seasonal Food (SEAS)" is a classification of nondurable goods that includes Fish (01.1.3), Fruit (01.1.6), and Vegetables (01.1.7).

Information provided in the notes pertaining to Special Aggregates HICP classifications can be found from the source at: http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/cache/metadata/en/prc_hicp_esms.htm.
